        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "You've always been good with computers, so going to CalTech for a degree in Computer Science just made sense. You would have preferred MIT, but CalTech accepted you. After graduating, you were recruited to work for the NSA as a security analyst. The work was boring, but you were good at it and the pay was also good. And in your off hours, you kept up the grey hat hacking you'd started in high school. Eventually your hacking led you into the dark web, where you found a forbiden server. Soon after, you were attacked by a monster.Your sire said the attack was random, a bungled feeding and an attack of conscience. But you know better. During your hacking, you found a valuable secret, something incredibly important to the war effort in Los Angeles. And you were caught. The trauma of the Embrace has driven the secret deep into your mind. You know your sire was just trying to save you, and you appreciate that. But being too near him only puts him in danger. You know your secret has to do with the New Promise Mandarinate, and after struggling with a group of archons, they are at a loss to do anything except send you to Los Angeles in hopes the Kindred there may be able to help."
